{"tid":2038508,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與何鴻燊合照裁走梁天琦 港大：照片經剪裁已補回原照","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T15:13:05.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7885c436ef89a302bf69d0d201601041f1f12ea5","tid":2038508,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"與何鴻燊合照裁走梁天琦 港大：照片經剪裁已補回原照<br />\n2020-05-27 HKT 22:42<br />\n<br />\n港大校長張翔昨日就商人何鴻燊逝世發文致以深切哀悼，新聞稿其中一張何鴻燊與港大學生的合照，本土民主前綫前發言人梁天琦被裁走。港大表示，絕對無意作出審查，並對造成任何誤解，感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n港大發言人表示，新聞稿及社交媒體所使用的相片，均經剪裁及拼貼，其中一張在2014年銘謝禮拍攝的照片，由於收到意見，已補上原照。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528751-20200527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528751-20200527.htm&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32axOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=a4e41e11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528751-20200527.htm&h=8eaaba4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528751-20200527.htm</a>"}]}